casebody.head_matter:
Robert B. MELSON
v.
DUNN, Comm'r, AL DOC, et al.
No. 16A1212.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 8, 2017.
The application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice Thomas and by him referred to the Court is denied. The order heretofore entered by Justice Thomas is vacated.
